    67	- **Layer discipline** — directionality grep gates that `harness/`, `_meta/`, and `scenarios/` never import `reference/` packages; only `adapters/reference/` may.
    68	- **Reference adapter** uses `secrets.token_hex` (not `token_urlsafe`) because the latter occasionally produces tokens starting with `-` that argparse interprets as a flag.
    69	- **Subscribe timeout** is set to 2.0s on the reference adapter so the timeout-path subscribe scenario completes quickly; chapter 7 §6.2's 30s is a SHOULD, so this is conformant.
